				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Player Characters comment on the book they just read - a dictionary of the Kozakuran language. \r\nIf they found the Szarr ring before, they notice the language is the same as the inscription on the Szarr Family Ring.\r\nIf they didn't find the ring, but recognized the language in the Ballroom dialog, then they recognize it.\r\nOtherwise they just say it's some ancient language."
